columns.name: Display Name
columns.formula:
concatenate(
  ifblank(
    [Special Name],
    ifblank(
      Text.Split(LineBreak()).first().Left(50).Trim(),
      [Resource Type].ToText()
    )
  )
    .ToText(),
  If(Topic.IsNotBlank(),Concatenate(" - ",Topic.ToText()),"")
)

format.action: ModifyRows(thisRow, [GPT Generated Resource], OpenAIprompt([Jon Dallas], Prompts.filter([Desired Output].contains([Topic Intro])).Prompt + Topic.totext() + LineBreak() + Prompts.filter([Desired Output].contains([Subtopic Intro])).Prompt + Subtopic.totext() + LineBreak() + Prompts.filter([Desired Output].totext().contains([Resource to Generate].totext())).Prompt.totext(), "gpt-3.5-turbo"))
ModifyRows(thisRow, [Date Last Updated], Today(), [Resource Status], Ready)

RUNACTIONS(
  activate(AddRow([Update Requests],[Event Resourc],thisRow)),
  ModifyRows(thisRow,[Resource Status],[Requires Update]))

RunActions(
  Image.Slice(2)
    .FormulaMap(
      AddRow(
        [Event Materials DB],
        Image,
        CurrentValue,
        Topic,
        Topic,
        [Resource Type],
        [Resource Type],
        [Media Type],
        [Media Type]
      )
    ),
    ModifyRows(
      thisRow,Image,Image.first()
    )
)
